metadata.name: Planet of the Dalai Llama
metadata.description:
Filled with the scent of a New York Pigeon candle, this planet is one of the calmest in the universe.  
Occasionally travelers would stop by, consulting about life, bringing goods from their home planet, and perhaps taking selfies with the lone owner of this planet. Some said it’s his fate, some said it’s mildly a curse, but to him he’s never a victim. Besides, with all of his favorite things surrounding him, what more can he ask?
